body_html: This sounds like the same issue as #13278. Could you add a comment there describing how you're building (Bazel? Linking against libtensorflow_framework.so? Linking against the C++ API .so?)? TensorFlow needs to use image libraries, but it's possible we can hide the symbols in some cases.
